data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis! Step inside this 5-bedroom masterpiece and discover a world of elegance. The comforting living areas create an inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment. The open-concept kitchen features a walk-in pantry, ample counter space with plenty of cabinets, and two rolling islands, offering a perfect start to make this house your home. The bedrooms are generously sized, providing plenty of room for rest and rejuvenation. The master suite is a sanctuary of its own. Complete with a luxurious attached bathroom and a walk-in closet. Outside, the compact yard provides endless possibilities, from hosting gatherings under the open skies to indulging in gardening passions. The detached garage is a bonus for your vehicle or hobbies. Located in the heart of Pahrump, this property offers the serenity of a suburban lifestyle while being close to city conveniences. RNDC has a Down Payment Assistance Program for First Time Homebuyers offering up to $25,000.00!
